    dc:description "Fig. 2. ♀♀ of Fanniidae Schnabel & Dziecicki, 1911. A. Fannia fuscula (Fallén, 1825), wing, ventral view. B. Same, detail of wing showing CS1‒3, ventral view. C. Same, detail of wing showing CS1‒3, dorsal view. D. Piezura pardalina Rondani, 1866, detail of wing showing CS1 in dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6784131/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6784135>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Australofannia spiniclunis Pont, 1977, ♀. A. Wing, ventral view. B. Detail of wing showing CS1‒3, ventral view. C. Detail of wing showing CS1‒3, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6784135/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6784137>
